ato (kumera), depending on the season and availability.","Add a red chilli to the soup in step 6 for added flavour.","This soup is a high source of protein, great for school lunches in a thermos.","Roast chickpeas in the oven for 15 minutes before milling for more flavour."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}